snippet.title: RECREATING KYLIE JENNERS MAKEUP ROUTINE | KYLIE JENNER EVERYDAY MAKEUP TUTORIAL | Amber Vazquez
snippet.description:
Hey guys! Today I recreated Kylie’s everyday makeup routine! I followed her old Snapchat tutorials that I found on YouTube. I hope you all enjoyed this video and be sure to subscribe so you don’t miss out on my future videos! 😊
